title: a message for the boys (and girls too)
itunes:author: Joey Kidney
itunes:subtitle: growing up with struggles
itunes:summary:
This is a message for the boys, and girls can listen in too don't worry. I tell the story of how i grew up with my struggles and battles, and where I am now. I hope this inspires some of you to live the life you have always wanted and to keep moving forward
